description:
※Click "cc" on the lower right menu to choose your subtitle language.

When the weather turns cold and frost forms on the ground, it’s time to make cured meats. Yunnan has many ways to preserve pork ribs: Shidian’s bone residue, Lijiang’s famous cured ribs, and wind-dried rib sausages stuffed into casings – all are mouthwatering just by name. For us, cured meats are the signature flavour of winter.

Hello, everyone! I am Dianxi Xiaoge, a Yunnan native. If you enjoy my videos, please keep subscribing to my channel. I'll continue to share my life and Yunnan-styled food in my uploads. Wish you have a happy life and enjoy tasty food every day
